  "detailed_description": "<strong>About this game</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/58022f7026c06d7095d20481dd875ba2.avif?t=1598951163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras_big/58022f7026c06d7095d20481dd875ba2.avif?t=1598951163 width=800 height=448 /></span><br>In this game you have to tactically use three students to fight against monsters and bosses who are coming to smash the castle of the game world. <br>Enjoy a variety of monsters and stages, step-by-step weapon upgrades, beautiful pixel graphics and animations right now!<br><br>This game created as a single game and it can run on PC and Android.<br><br><strong>Game Play</strong><br>Fight against the oncoming monsters to destroy your castle!<br>Defeat the monsters by making good use of the three weapons!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/448272937770763228b7427d52097f41.poster.avif?t=1598951163\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/448272937770763228b7427d52097f41.webm?t=1598951163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/448272937770763228b7427d52097f41.mp4?t=1598951163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game Stage</strong><br>Fight monsters in different stages like High Sky Forest, Uninhabited Snowfield, Andromeda Galaxy, and Devil's Playground!<br>Enjoy the game with different monsters and backgrounds for each wave!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/304fc4835b6317c3983ebdb3c90c0850.poster.avif?t=1598951163\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/304fc4835b6317c3983ebdb3c90c0850.webm?t=1598951163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/304fc4835b6317c3983ebdb3c90c0850.mp4?t=1598951163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>About this game</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/58022f7026c06d7095d20481dd875ba2.avif?t=1598951163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras_big/58022f7026c06d7095d20481dd875ba2.avif?t=1598951163 width=800 height=448 /></span><br>In this game you have to tactically use three students to fight against monsters and bosses who are coming to smash the castle of the game world. <br>Enjoy a variety of monsters and stages, step-by-step weapon upgrades, beautiful pixel graphics and animations right now!<br><br>This game created as a single game and it can run on PC and Android.<br><br><strong>Game Play</strong><br>Fight against the oncoming monsters to destroy your castle!<br>Defeat the monsters by making good use of the three weapons!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/448272937770763228b7427d52097f41.poster.avif?t=1598951163\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/448272937770763228b7427d52097f41.webm?t=1598951163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/448272937770763228b7427d52097f41.mp4?t=1598951163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game Stage</strong><br>Fight monsters in different stages like High Sky Forest, Uninhabited Snowfield, Andromeda Galaxy, and Devil's Playground!<br>Enjoy the game with different monsters and backgrounds for each wave!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374220/extras/304fc4835b6317c3983ebdb3c90c